foia:ProcessedRequestSection.foia:FootnoteText: * In the FY2010 FOIA Annual Report, EDA reported the number of requests pending at the end of FY2010 as “3.” This number was reported incorrectly. The correct number is “4.” Therefore, the number of requests pending as of the start of FY2011 has been amended to “4” in the FY2011 report.

** In the FY2010 FOIA Annual Report, NIST reported the number of requests pending at the end of FY2010 as “49.” This number was reported incorrectly. The correct number is “48.” Therefore, the number of requests pending as of the start of FY2011 has been amended to “48” in the FY2011 report.

*** In the FY2010 FOIA Annual Report, NOAA reported the number of requests pending at the end of FY2010 as “106.” This number was reported incorrectly. The correct number is “140.” Therefore, the number of requests pending as of the start of FY2011 has been amended to “140” in the FY2011 report.

*** In the FY2010 FOIA Annual Report, NTIA reported the number of requests pending at the end of FY2010 as “12.” This number was reported incorrectly. The correct number is “14.” Therefore, the number of requests pending as of the start of FY2011 has been amended to “14” in the FY2011 report.

***** In the FY2010 FOIA Annual Report, the number of requests pending at the end of FY2010 was reported as “267.” Due to the amendment in the number of requests pending as of the start of FY2011 for EDA, NIST, NOAA and NTIA (see footnotes above), the number of requests pending as of the start of FY2011 for the agency overall has been amended to “303.”
